    .panel#new-mission
      .new-mission
        div.new-mission__form
          h1 üéâ Let's plan the mission!
          label Give your mission a short and witty title
            input(type='text' name='mission_title' placeholder='Title of mission')
            span.--default 100 characters left
            span.--error 20 characters too many
          label Where should people meet?
            input(type='text' name='mission_location' placeholder='Find a place by address or name')
            span.--default Choose a safe and easily accessible location
            span.--error Sorry, that location wasn't found
          label So, what's the plan? Tell people about this mission.
            textarea(placeholder='What day and time will the mission start? How will other Miniheros recognise you? What other things should people know?')
            span.--default 200 characters left
            span.--error Give a little more info. 30 characters to go.
        div.new-mission__actions
          span 
            | 
          a.button(href='') Create Mission
    
    .panel#mission-created
      .modal
        div
          img(src='/img/location.svg' alt='')
          h1 Mission Created
          p You'll get an email on damirkotoric@gmail.com when people join your mission. Good work getting the idea out there!
          a.button.--expand(href='') Awesome! Go me.
  
